My name is Daniel and I represent Dazzini Studio. The biggest dubbing studio in Brazil specialized in dubbing for distance graduation and corporate training.
I am writing this email to you because in this new year of 2023 we want to invite you to be part of a new era in the development of our country. In the last 4 years Brazil was governed by a president who had no empathy towards minorities, low-income people or even those who have any disability whether physical, psychological or financial.
Dazzini Studio's main objective is to bring specialized knowledge to the greatest number of people in our country as a way to help rebuild our values through distance education. After 7 years of experience in the business, we have recorded over 5000 hours of audio aimed at the educational and corporate market for companies such as Linkedin, Amazon, Marriott, Microsoft, Burguer King and many others.
What we noticed after doing a lot of market research is that many students often feel unmotivated because a good part of the video material is in a language other than portuguese and, no matter how fluent the student is in the language or can follow the subtitles, the absorption of the content is not as effective as listening in your own language. Not to mention the huge audience that has some visual impairment and only has hearing to learn.
We want Coursera to be part of this story with us.
We know that Coursera is responsible for bringing thousands of students around the world the possibility of developing professionally through its online platforms.

As a finance officer, we would typically be required to work extensively with spreadsheets and financial data using Microsoft Excel. Here are some advanced Excel skills that can be particularly useful for finance officers:

Financial Modeling: we should be able to create financial models that can analyze and forecast data, generate charts, and conduct sensitivity analysis.

Advanced Functions and Formulas: we should be proficient in advanced Excel functions such as VLOOKUP, HLOOKUP, SUMIF, COUNTIF, INDEX, MATCH, and OFFSET, among others. These functions can help you automate tasks, analyze large data sets, and improve your productivity.

Pivot Tables and Charts: we should know how to use Pivot Tables and Pivot Charts to summarize and analyze complex data. You can create dashboards, reports, and other visualizations using these tools.

Macros and VBA: We should have a basic understanding of macros and Visual Basic for Applications (VBA) to automate repetitive tasks, generate customized reports, and enhance your efficiency.

Data Analysis: we should have strong data analysis skills and be familiar with statistical tools and techniques, such as regression analysis, correlation analysis, and hypothesis testing.

Data Visualization: We should know how to use Excel to create interactive and visually appealing charts, graphs, and other visualizations that can help you communicate your findings and insights to others.

These are just some of the advanced Excel skills that finance officers should have to be successful in their roles

Cytotec 200 mcg ® adalah obat aborsi ampuh yang berguna sebagai ramuan penggugur kandungan untuk usia kehamilan 1 bulan 2 bulan 3 bulan 4 bulan 5 bulan 6 bulan dan 7 ? 8 Bulan, obat aborsi cytotec 400mcg ini sudah terbukti manjur untuk menggugurkan kandungan (janin) dengan Cepat, Aman 100% Berhasil Tuntas Tanpa Kiret / Kuret.
Cytotec 200 mcg Berapa lama darah keluar setelah minum ?
Pendarahan paling banyak biasanya terjadi 4-8 jam setelah menggunakan dosis misoprostol yang pertama dan mulai berkurang dalam 24 jam. Beberapa perempuan mungkin akan melihat gumpalan dalam beberapa hari kedepan atau beberapa minggu, tergantung gumpalan yang dikeluarkan.
Cytotec apakah bahaya?
Cytotec ® tergolong sebagai obat aborsi yang berpotensi membahayakan kehamilan. Obat ini memicu kontraksi serta pendarahan pada rahim. Oleh karena itu, jangan minum obat Cytotec Asli® apabila Anda sedang hamil.

Apakah Perdarahan bisa Menyebabkan Keguguran?
Keguguran adalah kondisi meninggalnya janin di saat umur kehamilan masih di bawah 20 minggu. Keluarnya darah dari vagina adalah salah satu tanda keguguran. Meski demikian, terjadi perdarahan saat hamil bukan berarti Anda pasti mengalami keguguran.
Kenapa Janin Tidak Bisa Digugurkan?
Penyebab pasti dari tidak berkembangnya janin tersebut tidak diketahui. Hal ini diduga dikaitkan oleh kelainan kromosom yang terjadi di dalam sel telur yang dibuahi, hasil dari genetika atau sel telur dan sperma berkualitas rendah dan karena faktor kurangnya dosis yang diberikan saat aborsi, jadi untuk gugurkan kandungan harus sesuaikan dosis / jumlah obat aborsi sesusuai kebutuhan masing-masing janin apabila kandungan anda kuat diharuskan menggunakan paket tuntas 8 bulan yang disarankan dokter hallobunda.store
Apa Efek Samping Menggugurkan Kandungan?
Bila tidak dilakukan dengan benar atau menggunakan obat-obatan sembarangan, aborsi dapat menyebabkan kerusakan pada rahim dan vagina. Kerusakan ini dapat berupa lubang maupun luka berat pada dinding rahim, leher rahim, serta vagina, jadi konsultasikan dahulu dengan dokter terpercaya di hallobunda.store yang sudah terbukti dan membuktikan para pasiennya.

Dear Supplier,
Greetings from NIIT!

We are approaching you with a requirement from one of our Ultimate Client.

NIIT is being appointed by Ultimate Client as a Managed Service Provider for training requirements. 

We need a solution to upskill Ultimate Client employees with training on Supply Chain Management (After Sales).

Introduction
Competence assessment campaigns and resources reviews show that our population in Airbus commercial Customer Services domain needs to be upskilled in everything related to supply chain management in the frame of Aftersales.
That's why we would like to launch a training to add in our learning offer a set of learning solutions around supply chain management, logistics, inventory management and transport, all customized for the After Sales environment.

As is situation
Competence gaps identified in the business on supply chain management in After Sales (competence assessment campaigns + resources reviews).

Languages
French; English; German; Spanish

Expected situation
Business upskilled and driving efficient supply chain management activities

Learning objectives

1/ LEARNING SOLUTION(S) ON GENERAL CONTEXT OF SUPPLY CHAIN MANAGEMENT IN AFTER SALES 
a. Understand that effective supply chain management is critical to ensure the availability of spare parts, timely delivery of maintenance and repair services, and overall customer satisfaction. 
b. Be aware that effective supply chain management involves managing inventory levels, optimizing logistics and transportation, ensuring quality control and leveraging technology to improve efficiency and visibility throughout the supply chain.
Target proficiency levels: basic

2/ LEARNING SOLUTION(S) ON SUPPLY CHAIN MANAGEMENT IN AFTER SALES
a. Understand that Supply chain is governed by just-in-time processes, reduced repair cycles and after-sales performance commitments. 
b. Have an end to end view of the supply chain in after sales for the aeronautics industry: flow of goods, services and information from the manufacturer of aviation equipment and components to the customers. This includes managing the various activities involved in the delivery of spares parts, maintenance, repair and overhaul services, as well as managing the relationships with suppliers, distributors and service providers.
Target proficiency levels: basic

3/ LEARNING SOLUTION(S) ON LOGISTICS IN AFTER SALES
 Understand the importance of managing Logistics effectively, with a dedicated focus on the After Sales environment. 
Target proficiency levels: autonomous, advanced

4/ LEARNING SOLUTION(S) ON INVENTORY MANAGEMENT IN AFTER SALES
a. Understand the added value of efficiently managing the stock of spare parts and components required for maintenance, repair and overhaul (MRO) activities and be aware of its impact on the overall customer satisfaction.
b. Understand the need to maintain optimal inventory levels while minimizing excess stock and avoiding stockouts: this involves forecasting demand for spare parts, identifying critical components, tracking inventory levels and strategies to ensure the timely availability of parts.
c. Inventory analytics (theoretical & practical knowledge)  
Target proficiency levels: autonomous, advanced  

5/ LEARNING SOLUTION(S) ON TRANSPORT IN AFTER SALES
 a. Understand that transport is critical to the success of the after sales market, and that effective management of transportation can improve efficiency, reduce costs and enhance customer satisfaction. Understanding of different transport models (3PL/4PL).
 b. Transport in aftersales process: process mapping, analysis of workflows, process    efficiency measurement.
 c. Be aware of the stakes of transportation in the after sales market: 
- timeliness: timely transportation of parts and components is essential to minimize AOG, delays in transportation can affect customer satisfaction and revenue
- safety: transportation of parts and components must be handled with the utmost care to prevent damage, loss or theft. Special attention to safety regulations and procedures is needed.
- cost: what are the transportation costs impacts? highlight the need of optimizing routes, using the appropriate transportation modes and leveraging technology to improve transportation efficiency
- globalization: transportation includes crossing borders, dealing with customs regulations and complying with international laws and standards.
Target proficiency levels: autonomous, advanced  

6/ LEARNING SOLUTION(S) ON DIGITIZATION IN SUPPLY CHAIN
a.understanding how and ensuring that different supply chain tools work together to optimize process integration, bringing accurate data and processes together under one unified platform to provide end-to-end visibility
b.get to know different digitization techniques and tools
c.know and understand the stages of supply chain digitization
Target proficiency levels: basic, autonomous, advanced  

7/ LEARNING SOLUTION(S) ON SUPPLY CHAIN SUSTAINABILITY
a.Understand why sustainability is important in supply chain management (improve productivity while saving money at the same time. By using sustainable techniques and resources, you increase the efficiency of buildings, vehicles and machinery at a significant cost savings)
b.consider the environmental and human impact of the products' journey through the supply chain (from raw materials sourcing to production, storage, delivery and transportation)
Target proficiency levels: basic, autonomous, advanced  
8/ LEARNING SOLUTION(S) ON SUPPLIER DEVELOPMENT & MANAGEMENT IN AFTERMARKET CONTEXT
a.Supplier performance Monitoring : Understand the principles of monitoring supplier performance and the use of the different indicators to ensure suppliers meet the contractual and performance obligations (whether for MRO, logistics or warehouse providers)Understand how to steer, control and monitor supplier performance in aftermarket - assessing supplier performance, defining and setting expectations for quality and delivery, and maintaining relationships Know the basis of supplier relationship management (incl. supplier strategy,  managing vendor deliverables, working collaboratively to co-develop new processes, managing compliance as well as payment of invoices, ...) 
b.Supplier's excellence: How to ensure that suppliers meet or exceed Airbus Customer Services expectations in terms of quality, delivery, and cost.

Learning Format
Online; Classroom; Virtual classroom; Blended

Target Population
Customer Services employees in Airbus commercial, especially those dealing with Supply Chain topics (mainly white collars in SO, SM and Satair)

Number of Learners
2023: 50 to 100p expected. 2024: 50 to 100p expected.

Trainees level of expertise
Heterogeneous levels.
Most of them have basic level (especially on new topics like Supply Chain digitization or Supply Chain sustainability) or autonomous levels.
We would also need some advanced level trainings to develop our experts, in particular providing them with best practices from other companies.

We look forward to working with you to fulfill Ultimate Client's training requirements, please feel free to write me for any clarification required.

Regards,
Vikas Beniwal
